      <t>&lt;p&gt;The purpose of this document is to provide a catalogue of quality Network Training Materials for use by Internet trainers in training their users.  This memo provides information for the Internet community.  This memo does not specify an Internet standard of any kind.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
